		<p>Church Record, 1867-1891,1882-1904, 1897-1926; Recording Steward's
		  Book, 1901-1910; Sunday School records, 1896-1897, 1905; financial records,
		  1927-1965; membership register, 1965, publications, 1970s; and correspondence
		  and newsletters, 1970s-1987.</p> 
	 </scopecontent> 
